{"type":"article","id":292,"title":"比一比法轮功和海外民运人士的组织能力和影响力","uid":754,"topics":[],"contents":"<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/7b8xenr.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7b8xenr.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/7b8xenr.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/KNBsgq7.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/KNBsgq7.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/KNBsgq7.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/JcliMHy.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JcliMHy.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/JcliMHy.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/EEJstSp.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/EEJstSp.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/EEJstSp.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><b>首先是游行规模的对比，这是法轮功</b><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/JJHGJKT.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JJHGJKT.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/JJHGJKT.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/wWMBHEh.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/wWMBHEh.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/wWMBHEh.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/LzQjMtH.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LzQjMtH.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/LzQjMtH.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/JpvB3O4.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JpvB3O4.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/JpvB3O4.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<b>这是民运</b><br>\n<b>就组织游行能力和人数来讲，法轮功完胜</b><br>\n&nbsp;<br>\n&nbsp;<br>\n<b>第二我们来看看法轮功在国内搞些什么事</b><br>\n<b><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/tqqM6tC.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/tqqM6tC.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/tqqM6tC.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/dEitHc3.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/dEitHc3.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/dEitHc3.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/xZM42un.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/xZM42un.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/xZM42un.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a></b><br>\n<b><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/eqwcl4G.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/eqwcl4G.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/eqwcl4G.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>.</b><br>\n<b>法轮功动用在国内的资源，将标语打印到人民币上，多数民众都收过这种钱币，部分民众接到过法轮功打来宣传电话或者发来的宣传手册，以及偶尔会在一些地方看到过标语</b><br>\n<b>网民在13年前时不时可以在网上见到有轮子发翻墙软件。并且大量网民有使用过法轮功背景的翻墙软件的历史。</b><br>\n&nbsp;<br>\n<b>而民运人士&nbsp;</b><br>\n<b><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/Vbtit3l.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Vbtit3l.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Vbtit3l.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a></b><br>\n<b><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/kfjImN1.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/kfjImN1.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/kfjImN1.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a></b><br>\n<b><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/is8jSsq.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/is8jSsq.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/is8jSsq.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a></b><br>\n<b>有极少数人能见到民运人士拉横幅，就国内知名度来讲，民运人士跟法轮功差得远。</b><br>\n<b>但是民运人士在反贼网民中知名度比较高，并且更能博得好感</b><br>\n<br>\n&nbsp;<br>\n<b>我们来比比法轮功和民运人士相关（不一定是创办）的媒体</b><br>\n&nbsp;<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/K3Rn91K.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/K3Rn91K.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/K3Rn91K.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n&nbsp;<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/FE54jbQ.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/FE54jbQ.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/FE54jbQ.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<b>可以很明显看得出来这些法轮功背景的网站设计的都极丑，可能就新唐人设计的还像点样，并且喜欢发一些来路不明未经证实的新闻来博人眼球，可能跟受众面有关</b><br>\n&nbsp;<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/yJkJ60h.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/yJkJ60h.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/yJkJ60h.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n&nbsp;<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/la6yCQy.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/la6yCQy.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/la6yCQy.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n&nbsp;<br>\n<b>而民运人士相关的，也就是这些民运人士经常露脸并且有合作的网站设计的更加好看，消息来源比轮子的网站要更加信得过一些， 在反贼网民中接受度更高</b>","date":"2019-01-04","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":0}